    "updated_at": "2020-11-12T09:22:40Z",
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "It is blocking for us to move to truffle atm. We are using an async method to get the private key used to instantiate the `HDWalletProvider`:\r\n\r\n```\r\nstaging: {\r\n      provider: async () => {\r\n        const { pkey, infuraKey } = await getKeys();\r\n        return new HDWalletProvider(pkey, `https://mainnet.infura.io/v3/${infuraKey}`);\r\n      },\r\n      network_id: 1, // mainnet\r\n      gas: _gasLimit,\r\n      gasPrice: _gasPrice,\r\n    },\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis async method is [here](https://github.com/argentlabs/argent-contracts/blob/develop/utils/private-key-loader.js), getting the key from AWS. \r\n\r\n\r\n",
